ing: 1 (15 ounce) can pinto beans, drained and rinsed
1 (15 ounce) can black beans, rinsed and drained
1 1/2 cups shredded Cheddar and Monterey cheese blend
des: "This is an unusual salad that everyone in my office loves.  I get requests for it time and time again."
ins: In a large bowl, combine the pinto beans, black beans, cheese, lettuce and tomatoes. Add 3/4 bottle dressing and mix well. Add corn chips before serving.
